node.title: Matamata crash: Three children remain in critical condition
node.description: Three of the five children involved in a crash in Matamata remain in a critical condition.
node.content:
["Three of the five children involved in a crash in Matamata remain in a critical condition.", "", "
Waikato Hospital Photo: RNZ / Simon Rogers
", "A car was found in a ditch off Morrinsville-Walton Road on Monday night.", "Five children, aged from 10 to 13, were all injured in the accident.", "One was transferred to Starship Hospital in a critical condition, and two remain in a critical condition at Waikato Hospital.", "Another is in a serious but stable condition, and the fifth child is in a stable condition.", "Police said they are continuing to make enquiries into the circumstances of the crash."]
